<main class="content">
      <a href='/'>Return to Home</a>

      <h1>Find students that are in need of your expertise</h1>
      <p>Once you enter a class that you can help with, a list of students will come up along with pertanent info for each. We encourage you to send an emails to students that you think may be a good fit to inquire if they would be interested!</p>

      <aside class="filter-container">
          <h2>Filters</h2>

          <div class="filter-input-container">
            <label for="filter-text" class="filter-input-label">College:</label>
            <div class="filter-input-element">
              <input type="text" name="filter-text" id="filter-text" class="filter-input">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="filter-input-container">
            <label for="filter-text" class="filter-input-label">Classes:</label>
            <div class="filter-input-element">
              <input type="text" name="filter-text" id="filter-text" class="filter-input">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="filter-input-container">
            <label for="filter-min-price" class="filter-input-label">Budget:</label>
            <div class="filter-input-element">
              <input type="text" name="filter-min-price" id="filter-min-price" class="filter-input" placeholder="min">
            </div>
            <div class="filter-input-element">
              <input type="text" name="filter-max-price" id="filter-max-price" class="filter-input" placeholder="max">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="filter-input-container">
            <label for="filter-city" class="filter-input-label">Year in School:</label>
            <div class="filter-input-element">
              <select id="filter-city" class="filter-input" name="filter-city">
                <option selected value="">Any</option>
                <option>Freshman</option>
                <option>Sophomore</option>
                <option>Junior</option>
                <option>Senior</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <br>
  
          <button id="filter-update-button" class="action-button">Search</button>
        </aside>
        
    </main>